Type; Defense
Requires the ground to be normal terrain

Armour Up.  Cracks the ground under the character.
Gain armour.

Earth wall.
Puts up a wall in a 3x1 area.  Short range.  Requires undamaged ground.

Entomb
Crack the ground all around an enemy to remove them from play for a turn

Earthshaker
Pulls enemies in a straight line one square towards you